headline: Latest News In E-Commerce - Heat-Resistant Packaging Revolutionizes Temperature-Sensitive Product Delivery
summary: Recent developments in the e-commerce sector highlight significant advancements in the heat-resistant packaging market, as rising online sales of temperature-sensitive products such as food and pharmaceuticals drive demand. headline: Stocks Slip Before the Open With Focus on U.S. Economic Data and Fed Speak
summary: December S&P 500 E-Mini futures (ESZ25) are down -0.06%, and December Nasdaq 100 E-Mini futures (NQZ25) are down -0.12% this morning as investors await a fresh batch of U.S. economic data, remarks from Federal Reserve officials, and an earnings report from bulk retailer Costco.
